{"tid":627837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1998年　美元加息升值　熱錢抽離香港　樓價大跌　樓市崩潰　無關供應","createTime":"2018-04-13T10:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T05:17:55.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8059ad8a4306be299f270ee186d878587a39396","tid":627837,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://luan-invest.blogspot.hk/2015/04/2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fluan-invest.blogspot.hk%2F2015%2F04%2F2.html&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGsnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=0c61210e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://luan-invest.blogspot.hk/2015/04/2.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一種講法，美元上升，香港樓價會跌，現在美元正在上升週期，香港樓價會否下跌？看圖二，兩者又的確有點關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LmRqWs5O6dw/VRyxfSwwxaI/AAAAAAAACOA/e1t8li28NUw/s1600/Hong%2BKong%2BProperty%2BPrice%2Band%2BUS%2Bdollar%2Brising%2Btrend.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LmRqWs5O6dw%2FVRyxfSwwxaI%2FAAAAAAAACOA%2Fe1t8li28NUw%2Fs1600%2FHong%252BKong%252BProperty%252BPrice%252Band%252BUS%252Bdollar%252Brising%252Btrend.jpg&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGsnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=8d521138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LmRqWs5O6dw/VRyxfSwwxaI/AAAAAAAACOA/e1t8li28NUw/s1600/Hong%2BKong%2BProperty%2BPrice%2Band%2BUS%2Bdollar%2Brising%2Btrend.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n美元上升對香港樓價的影響只是表象，實質上，美元上升影響熱錢流向才是真正原因，而左右熱錢的流向，是國際市場拆借美元的利率即倫敦同業拆息(LIBOR)和香港同業拆息(HIBOR)之間的差距(spread)。<br />\n<br />\n由於聯系匯率，港元與美元掛鈎，理論上HIBOR的趨勢必須跟隨LIBOR，在一般情下HIBOR與LIBOR的走勢一致，基本上差距很窄(見圖三)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-86v0nN9xrGg/VRyz42_78BI/AAAAAAAACOw/ZpjvWiK8LaQ/s1600/3-month%2BLibor%2Band%2B3-month%2Bhibor.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-86v0nN9xrGg%2FVRyz42_78BI%2FAAAAAAAACOw%2FZpjvWiK8LaQ%2Fs1600%2F3-month%252BLibor%252Band%252B3-month%252Bhibor.jpg&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGsnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=19f4527f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-86v0nN9xrGg/VRyz42_78BI/AAAAAAAACOw/ZpjvWiK8LaQ/s1600/3-month%2BLibor%2Band%2B3-month%2Bhibor.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"0d5d32e11b6610a0a4db44b3dc37655bade93504","tid":627837,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"今次經濟危機同以前都係一樣原因，唔同嘅係有個政權想拼死一搏，因為佢唔搏唔係經濟衰退，係四分五裂"},{"pid":"6a345cf21981078f2b19ea5a00fd51a46cc66fee","tid":627837,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"都未放大陸人落黎，你知唔知上面購買力仲係好大。"},{"pid":"f61dfaecd619d5b8f5d8bf2050dc56316094c358","tid":627837,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a345cf21981078f2b19ea5a00fd51a46cc66fee","tid":627837,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"都未放大陸人落黎，你知唔知上面購買力仲係好大。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"剛需剛需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433b182143bb3c64c29ab46dc52090dc93500981","tid":627837,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"香港樓市將成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時十萬蚊呎"}]}